                  ʾabuna
               </foaf:name><crm:P4_has_time_span><crm:E52_Time-span><crm:P78_is_identified_by/></crm:E52_Time-span></crm:P4_has_time_span><crm:P4_has_time_span><crm:E52_Time-span><crm:P78_is_identified_by> He was a monk who is said in his Miracles to have been the son of 
                  Yǝkunno ʾAmlāk and a spiritual disciple of  a certain 
                  
                  
                    ʾabbā  Yoḥannǝs Kamā. 
                  He left the secular life during the reign 
                  of King Wǝdǝm Raʿad. </crm:P78_is_identified_by></crm:E52_Time-span></crm:P4_has_time_span><snap:occupation>16th century abbot of May Barāzyo (Tigray)</snap:occupation></rdf:Description><rdf:Description rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS1640Alaniqos"><snap:hasBond rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/bond/AllianceWith-https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11248YohannesKama"/></rdf:Description><rdf:Description rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/bond/AllianceWith-https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11248YohannesKama"><rdf:type rdf:resource="http://data.snapdrgn.net/ontology/snap#AllianceWith"/><snap:bond-with rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11248YohannesKama"/></rdf:Description><rdf:Description rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS1640Alaniqos"><snap:hasBond rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/bond/AllianceWith-https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10303Yekunno"/></rdf:Description><rdf:Description rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/bond/AllianceWith-https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10303Yekunno"><rdf:type rdf:resource="http://data.snapdrgn.net/ontology/snap#AllianceWith"/><snap:bond-with rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10303Yekunno"/></rdf:Description><rdf:Description rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS1640Alaniqos"><snap:hasBond rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/bond/BrotherOf-https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10111WedemR"/></rdf:Description><rdf:Description rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/bond/BrotherOf-https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10111WedemR"><rdf:type rdf:resource="http://data.snapdrgn.net/ontology/snap#BrotherOf"/><snap:bond-with rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10111WedemR"/></rdf:Description><rdf:Description rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS1640Alaniqos"><ecrm:P129i_is_subject_of rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4049GadlaAl"/></rdf:Description><oa:Annotation rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS1640Alaniqos/person/annotation/1"><oa:hasTarget rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS1640Alaniqos"/><oa:hasBody rdf:resource="https://